279
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:02,120
And you too, why do you even bother with him?

280
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:04,280
Seriously.

281
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:10,840
<i>After the shoot, come to Room 1638
at the Grand Hyatt by yourself.</i>

282
00:20:10,840 --> 00:20:12,590
<i>I'll be waiting for you there.</i>

283
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:16,760
Let's go.

284
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:50,720
Okay, let's leave it at that.

285
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,760
Surprised to see me here?

286
00:20:52,760 --> 00:20:54,486
The crew's hotel is full of prying eyes.

287
00:20:54,486 --> 00:20:56,993
It's safer to talk here.

288
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:06,002
Does my earring look good?

289
00:21:06,959 --> 00:21:08,800
Was that really necessary?

290
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:10,999
I wanted to be just like you.

291
00:21:10,999 --> 00:21:13,079
But it really hurt.

292
00:21:13,840 --> 00:21:17,040
I only endured it by thinking of you.

293
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:23,519
Hey, I'm the one who paid for this room.

294
00:21:23,519 --> 00:21:26,070
Can you two wait until I'm gone
before you start flirting?

295
00:21:27,159 --> 00:21:28,639
So...

296
00:21:28,639 --> 00:21:31,280
what exactly is all this?

297
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:35,720
Someone insisted that
I explain it to you myself.

298
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:37,200
The marriage news is fake.

299
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,840
The trending search was bought by a rival.

300
00:21:38,840 --> 00:21:41,280
I hope you don't overthink it.

301
00:21:41,280 --> 00:21:42,479
I won't.

302
00:21:42,479 --> 00:21:44,959
I never take gossip to heart.

303
00:21:44,959 --> 00:21:48,120
But... I should still thank you.

304
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:49,360
No need.

305
00:21:49,360 --> 00:21:50,760
I'm a woman of my word.

306
00:21:50,760 --> 00:21:53,119
If I promise something, I'll get it done.

307
00:21:53,119 --> 00:21:54,919
Look at how worried you were.

308
00:21:54,919 --> 00:21:56,192
See?

309
00:21:56,192 --> 00:21:58,548
He's much more mature and calm than you.

310
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:04,120
Fine.

311
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:06,952
I'll stop being a third wheel.

312
00:22:06,952 --> 00:22:09,999
By the way, I've already handled the media.

313
00:22:09,999 --> 00:22:11,919
I hope this little episode...

314
00:22:11,919 --> 00:22:14,679
won't affect our agreement.

315
00:22:16,999 --> 00:22:18,521
I'm off.

316
00:22:21,879 --> 00:22:24,039
What agreement do you have?

317
00:22:29,559 --> 00:22:32,120
We're in the same industry.

318
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:33,800
What other agreement could there be?

319
00:22:33,800 --> 00:22:36,000
Just a clean break.

320
00:22:37,120 --> 00:22:38,760
Come on.

321
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:02,010
Are you still acting?

322
00:23:03,559 --> 00:23:06,040
Don't you think...

323
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:08,879
we're more dramatic than the movie?

324
00:23:13,800 --> 00:23:15,599
What are you doing?

325
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:17,439
Try it.

326
00:23:17,439 --> 00:23:19,519
Savor the red wine.

327
00:23:24,788 --> 00:23:27,542
[Gao Zhun]

328
00:23:48,840 --> 00:23:50,393
Hello, Senior.

329
00:23:50,393 --> 00:23:53,597
It's me, Fang Chi.

330
00:23:53,597 --> 00:23:56,720
I recall you have a clinic in the CBD.

331
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:59,200
Could I borrow it for a while?

332
00:24:01,279 --> 00:24:02,999
Okay.

333
00:24:02,999 --> 00:24:04,471
Thank you, Senior.

334
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:25,439
Ms. Feng.

335
00:24:25,439 --> 00:24:28,240
Please inform all patients except Gao Zhun

336
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,600
that starting next week,

337
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:31,418
treatment will be at a new location.

338
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:35,506
I'll send you the address later.

339
00:24:43,698 --> 00:24:45,804
[Gao Zhun: Can I go over to you earlier today?]

340
00:24:45,804 --> 00:24:48,165
[Unpin]

341
00:25:29,840 --> 00:25:30,999
Hello?

342
00:25:30,999 --> 00:25:33,160
D-Dr. Fang.

343
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:34,879
You finally picked up.

344
00:25:34,879 --> 00:25:36,668
Where have you been?

345
00:25:36,668 --> 00:25:40,120
Why is your house empty,
and the clinic cleared out?

346
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:43,360
Did something happen to you?

347
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:49,420
<i>Why...</i>

348
00:25:50,046 --> 00:25:52,006
<i>Why aren't you saying anything?</i>

349
00:25:57,680 --> 00:25:59,640
Are you...

350
00:26:02,359 --> 00:26:04,599
abandoning me?

351
00:26:08,080 --> 00:26:10,121
Mr. Gao.

352
00:26:12,040 --> 00:26:14,780
Your treatment is over.

353
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:18,780
<i>But I'm not cured yet.</i>

354
00:26:20,799 --> 00:26:23,439
Your nightmare no longer exists.

355
00:26:24,999 --> 00:26:26,839
<i>Mr. Gao.</i>

356
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:30,509
<i>You'll get better in time.</i>

357
00:26:32,399 --> 00:26:34,120
Can you let me meet you?

358
00:26:34,120 --> 00:26:37,959
Whatever we have to say,
let's say it face to face.

359
00:26:37,959 --> 00:26:39,314
I'm sorry.

360
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:42,480
That wouldn't be appropriate.

361
00:26:43,399 --> 00:26:44,839
<i>I'm the doctor.</i>

362
00:26:44,839 --> 00:26:46,759
<i>You're the patient.</i>

363
00:26:47,879 --> 00:26:49,599
I've already...

364
00:26:54,439 --> 00:26:55,999
made too many mistakes.

365
00:26:55,999 --> 00:26:58,439
<i>You're not in the wrong. I was willing.</i>

366
00:26:58,439 --> 00:27:00,000
Enough.

367
00:27:02,040 --> 00:27:03,240
<i>Gao Zhun.</i>

368
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:05,280
<i>Listen to me carefully.</i>

369
00:27:06,999 --> 00:27:09,421
It's time for you to move on.

370
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:14,200
Do you mean...

371
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:17,360
it's over between us?

372
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:25,960
When did we ever start?

373
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:30,999
<i>Just treat it as a dream.</i>

374
00:27:30,999 --> 00:27:32,080
No.

375
00:27:32,080 --> 00:27:35,120
If this is a dream, I can't wake up.

376
00:27:36,080 --> 00:27:37,120
<i>I'm begging you.</i>

377
00:27:37,120 --> 00:27:40,239
<i>D-Don't leave me.</i>

378
00:27:40,239 --> 00:27:41,279
<i>Once a week.</i>

379
00:27:41,279 --> 00:27:44,279
<i>Even once every two weeks is fine.</i>

380
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,040
I won't like you anymore.

381
00:27:47,040 --> 00:27:49,280
I'll stop liking you, okay?

382
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:52,963
Just let me see you. Don't leave me.

383
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:42,455
<i>Don't... Don't force me.</i>

384
00:28:55,320 --> 00:28:57,200
<i>Don't...</i>

385
00:28:58,278 --> 00:29:00,198
We can't...

386
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:07,389
keep making the same mistakes.

387
00:29:14,879 --> 00:29:16,406
Cut.

388
00:29:19,226 --> 00:29:21,000
Where is he?

389
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,360
He was crying too hard.

390
00:29:22,360 --> 00:29:24,840
He went to the restroom to calm down.

391
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,839
Don't do this.

392
00:29:48,839 --> 00:29:50,959
There are people outside.

393
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,793
Your eyes are all red from crying.

394
00:30:01,740 --> 00:30:03,520
The movie is fiction.

395
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:05,842
But you and I are real.

396
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:13,080
I know.

397
00:30:15,319 --> 00:30:16,680
But Gao Zhun's pain...

398
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,938
I...

399
00:30:19,320 --> 00:30:20,805
I understand it completely.

400
00:30:21,799 --> 00:30:23,999
If you understand Gao Zhun,

401
00:30:25,120 --> 00:30:27,593
then you should know even better...

402
00:30:27,593 --> 00:30:30,256
that Fang Chi's love for him never changed.

403
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:36,079
And off-camera, I have always loved you, too.

404
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:47,160
Is he urging us to re-shoot a scene?

405
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,839
No.

406
00:30:48,839 --> 00:30:50,799
It's Feng Yun Ting.

407
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:05,966
My engagement and marriage to Mr. Zhen...

408
00:31:05,966 --> 00:31:08,359
are both completely groundless.

409
00:31:08,359 --> 00:31:11,760
Regarding the so-called exposé,
the police are now involved.

410
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:13,820
Is this just your side of the story?

411
00:31:13,820 --> 00:31:16,620
Does Mr. Zhen feel the same way?

412
00:31:17,239 --> 00:31:22,000
In fact, Zhen Xin and I have already broken up.

413
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:26,800
Regarding the fake news of our marriage,

414
00:31:26,800 --> 00:31:30,120
we have both given it a lot of thought.

415
00:31:30,120 --> 00:31:34,359
As for this relationship,
we both need some space.

416
00:31:34,359 --> 00:31:37,439
May I ask who initiated the breakup?

417
00:31:37,439 --> 00:31:39,440
It was me.

418
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:41,301
He agreed to it.

419
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:49,240
That must have been your agreement.

420
00:31:52,439 --> 00:31:55,200
- Ms. Feng has really been wronged.
- Zhang Zhun.

421
00:31:57,359 --> 00:32:00,359
There's something I must tell you in person.

422
00:32:02,812 --> 00:32:04,390
I love you.

423
00:32:06,040 --> 00:32:07,839
Not as Fang Chi.

424
00:32:07,839 --> 00:32:09,600
But as me.

425
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:11,880
Zhen Xin truly loves you.

426
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:26,340
I know.

427
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:30,680
I love you, too.

428
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,468
<i>I'm at the production crew's hotel.</i>

429
00:32:47,468 --> 00:32:48,480
<i>Give me your room number.</i>

430
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:50,240
<i>I'm coming to see you.</i>

431
00:32:53,520 --> 00:32:56,200
<i>What are you doing here?</i>

432
00:32:56,200 --> 00:32:58,560
<i>Is something the matter?</i>

433
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:02,640
<i>"Best Actor Zhen Xin's change of heart on set."</i>

434
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:04,439
<i>"The third party is actually a man."</i>

435
00:33:04,439 --> 00:33:06,160
<i>"Zhen Xin and Zhang Zhun bond over filming."</i>

436
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:08,200
<i>"Matching earrings on their left ears."</i>

437
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:11,320
<i>Who's Zhang Zhun?
The matching earrings are hilarious.</i>

438
00:33:11,320 --> 00:33:13,000
<i>No one would care if he didn't
try to hype himself up, okay?</i>

439
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:15,759
<i>If Zhen Xin is gay,
I'm seriously going to stop being a fan.</i>

440
00:33:15,759 --> 00:33:17,159
<i>That's so disgusting.</i>

441
00:33:17,159 --> 00:33:19,840
<i>Nowadays, every guy tries to get famous
by selling a "bromance" narrative.</i>

442
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:22,360
<i>Please dig up some dirt on this Zhang Zhun.</i>

443
00:37:37,279 --> 00:37:38,400
Last night...

444
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:41,120
I actually had a gift for you.

445
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:45,720
Pick one.

446
00:37:47,680 --> 00:37:48,840
Choose carefully.

447
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:51,480
This is the first gift I'll be giving you.

448
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:53,354
Oh.

449
00:38:06,919 --> 00:38:08,679
I'll take this one.

450
00:38:09,319 --> 00:38:11,480
These two are a pair.

451
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:13,719
You and I will wear a pair.

